alerts.description:
There is a risk of thaw (Level 2 of 3).
Runoff: 30-45 l/m²

There is a risk of wind gusts (level 1 of 4).
Height range: > 600 m; Max. gusts: ~ 60 km/h; Wind direction: south-west then west; Increased gusts: in exposed locations < 70 km/h

There is a risk of storm-force gusts (Level 2 of 4).
Height range: > 1000 m; Max. gusts: 75-95 km/h; Wind direction: south-west then west

There is a risk of heavy persistent rain (Level 3 of 4).
Precipitation amounts: 40-60 l/m²; in windward areas: < 70 l/m²
